                  "excerpt": "Has the potential to individually affect each ore type in a vein when hitting the special narrow brackets. This will be indicated with the \"2x\" icon near the name of the affected ore after mining the vein. The same applies to fishing and capturing wildlife, potentially giving you 2x fish or 2x/4x/6x tags on bad/good/perfect wildlife captures. Also may yield double the plants from harvesting."
